        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 24 at 6:58PM EDT until June 24 at 7:45PM EDT by NWS Detroit/Pontiac MI</headline>
        <description>At 658 PM EDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Mayville,
moving northeast at 40 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

This severe storm will be near...
Kingston around 705 PM EDT.

Other locations impacted by this severe thunderstorm include East
Dayton, Tuscola, Wisner, Gilford, Silverwood, Watrousville,
Richville, Fostoria, and Bay Park.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
